eastern world. However I ask as well...

Whaddya HEL *giggles* it have to do with Samurai History?!?!?!?

Octavio Augusto Okimoto Alves de Carvalho
São Paulo - SP Brazil
(And I am not an icelandic, it is just what I would call here as my Homyô in
an aproximated translation)
